down the turmoil 
this time the kremlin first tried the power of persuasion 
gorbachev made a personal appeal feb 26 for civic maturity and 
restraint and the mass demonstrations in yerevan subsided but 
two days later a riot broke out in the azerbaijani city of 
sumgait and at least 32 people were killed 26 of them armenians 
the kremlin also tried changing the local leadership installing 
new party chiefs in armenia and azerbaijan the new officials 
quickly acknowledged that armenians in nagornokarabakh had been 
deprived culturally and socially under previous regimes 
