divisions will not be affected by the shutdown he said 
the move will help consolidate vacation expenses in the third 
quarter which will improve cash flow in the fourth quarter when 
we want to do well charland said its hard to say what that 
means because so much of our business is concentrated at the end 
of the year 
control data has closed some of its operations temporarily 
before but this is the first time it has done so this year 
charland said the most recent shutdown occurred last year in the 
government systems group which makes military computers he said 
